des:
Docol smart home skill allows you to control Docol Smart products, currently Doc Vox Docol smart faucet.

With Doc Vox, you can open and close, dispense precise amounts of water, and use presets to customize your experience. You can say "Alexa open faucet" and Doc Vox will dispense water without any touch.

Docol Smart Home is a growing collection of connected products that provide voice experiences through your favorite Alexa device.

It will be necessary to create an account through "Docol Produtos Conectados" app to authenticate in "Docol smart home" Skill. You can follow these steps:
1. Download “Docol Produtos Conectados” app from Android or IOS app store;
2. Create an account in “Docol Produtos Conectados” app;
3. You will need Docol smart product on hand;
4. Configure this smart Docol product in “Docol Produtos Conectados” app and change the appropriate name that will be used in “Docol smart home” Skill;
5. Download “Alexa” app from Android or IOS app store;
6. Search Skill “Docol Smart Home” from Skills in “Alexa” app;
7. Click Enable Skill “Docol Smart Home”, and you will be navigated to login page;
8. Follow the instructions on the page to complete the linking;
9. Now all setup is complete. You can enjoy voice control on your smart Docol products:
“Alexa, open faucet.”
“Alexa, close faucet.”
“Alexa, set faucet to 2.”

Developed by Docol.
